104 (3) The ride share network service ensures that each ride share driver holds a for-hire
105 license endorsement pursuant to Code Section 40-5-39 or obtains a private background
106 check certification as described in such Code section at least once every two years.
107 (b) Any digital network or internet network used by a ride share network service shall be
108 considered a service and shall not qualify as a product."
